title: Dog And Beth On The Hunt S02E17 Birthday Special Part Two WS DSR
description:
The surprises continue as the craziness of the Chapman party draws near. Tension rises as Beth desperately hurries to complete all her secret plans for Dog's surprise birthday party. As the big day draws near, Chris, Leland and Dakota decide to create a new surprise of their own -- a striptease from Chris. Will the party go off without a hitch? Or will Chris' striptease ruin everything Beth has been planning?
